  "texts": [
    "The three websites share many other similarities.",
    "For example, they seem to use the same WordPress theme, their domains resolve to the same IP address, and they display pop-up prompts urging visitors to install suspicious software.",
    "Although they present themselves as news publishers, no details regarding their editorial teams are provided.",
    "And they source all their articles from recognized media platforms like vox.com and forbes.com.",
    "Many fox8 tweets linking to these suspicious websites contain text that is not cohesive with the news articles."
